log
@remove #ifndef __MirBSD__ before setlocale(); related changes
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: chmod.c,v 1.18 2004/07/01 18:25:47 otto Exp $	*/
/*	$NetBSD: chmod.c,v 1.12 1995/03/21 09:02:09 cgd Exp $	*/

